@page "/"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>Plan2Gather - Stop guessing, start gathering.</PageTitle>

<div class="text-center welcome-section">
    <h2 class="display-5">Stop guessing, start gathering.</h2>
    <p class="lead mt-3">
        Plan2Gather finds the perfect time for everyone.<br />
        Share a link, mark your availability, and let the grid show you exactly when your crew can meet.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-orange btn-lg">Create an account</a>
    </div>
</div>

<hr class="my-5" />

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>📅 1. Create an Event</h3>
        <p>Choose dates and time windows. Get a unique shareable link instantly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>🔗 2. Share the Link</h3>
        <p>Send it to anyone – no account needed for guests.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>✅ 3. Find the Best Time</h3>
        <p>See overlapping availabilities and pick the perfect hangout moment.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Everything you need to plan</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
        <h3>📊 Visual Availability Grid</h3>
        <p>See at a glance when everyone is free. Color-coded overlap shows the best windows for your whole group.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
        <h3>🔗 Share with a Link</h3>
        <p>Send one link. Guests can respond without creating an account — your full team in one place, effortlessly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
        <h3>🌍 Timezone Aware</h3>
        <p>Every attendee sees times in their own timezone. No more mental math or 3am scheduling mistakes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
        <h3>🎛️ Host Controls</h3>
        <p>As host, manage your guest list, remove unavailable attendees, and lock the final meeting time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
        <h3>🔔 Smart Notifications</h3>
        <p>Get notified when the host finalizes the meeting time. No more refreshing the page wondering if it's decided.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
        <h3>📋 Your Events Dashboard</h3>
        <p>Track every event you've created or joined. See pending responses, finalized times, and meeting details in one view.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="text-center mt-4">
    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-orange btn-lg">Create your Free Account</a>
</div>